    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "advantages_text",
      "x": 812.8054298642534,
      "y": 28.099547511312217,
      "width": 208.1447963800905,
      "height": 117.6470588235294,
      "text": "✅ Advantages\n\n• Fully autonomous — no human wait time\n• Consistent decisions based on\n  doc-to-skill alignment\n• Runs 24/7, scales to any course\n• Can retry autonomously if\n  too few skills found\n• Teacher domain knowledge\n  encoded in agent prompt",
      "originalText": "✅ Advantages\n\n• Fully autonomous — no human wait time\n• Consistent decisions based on\n  doc-to-skill alignment\n• Runs 24/7, scales to any course\n• Can retry autonomously if\n  too few skills found\n• Teacher domain knowledge\n  encoded in agent prompt",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#047857",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
