    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "drawbacks_text",
      "x": 812.8054298642534,
      "y": 184.20814479638008,
      "width": 208.1447963800905,
      "height": 140.2714932126697,
      "text": "⚠️ Drawbacks\n\n• Teacher's tacit knowledge lost\n  (e.g. \"skip frontend for this cohort\")\n• Hard to debug: long agentic chains\n  fail silently\n• Bridge uses threading — fragile\n  under event loop conflicts\n• Deep Agent may hallucinate\n  teacher preferences\n• Notebook showed\n  \"No structured_response found\"\n  — real production failure\n• Each extra hop adds latency\n  + token cost",
      "originalText": "⚠️ Drawbacks\n\n• Teacher's tacit knowledge lost\n  (e.g. \"skip frontend for this cohort\")\n• Hard to debug: long agentic chains\n  fail silently\n• Bridge uses threading — fragile\n  under event loop conflicts\n• Deep Agent may hallucinate\n  teacher preferences\n• Notebook showed\n  \"No structured_response found\"\n  — real production failure\n• Each extra hop adds latency\n  + token cost",
      "fontSize": 10,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#dc2626",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
